{
  "stem": "13313.5",
  "chunk_idx": 15,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the irony was that the policeman could not understand why I was upset.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They didn't understand why the swastika was so provocative.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My wife says, why did they-- why are you keeping my husband?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They says, well, because he says there's no room for swastikas in Canada.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He asked me if I'm normal, if I'm excited, if I have disturbances.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I says, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I'm perfectly normal.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I know exactly what I'm doing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I says, but I think you people don't know what, what this is all about.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So one of them stayed with me downstairs.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "As a matter fact, I went-- I told him, sit down.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Relax.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We can talk.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He says, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I'm not supposed to sit down because I have a prisoner.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I'm supposed to stand.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I says, can, can I go and tell my wife what, what, what what's happened, that I'm OK?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You can't go.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So they send someone else.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I says-- and he couldn't understand why I was upset.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Now, that's the message.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "How can a policeman that are assigned to watch over an Israeli president of a Jewish people, our people there, not understand what a swastika is all about?",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Germany, the swastika is forbidden.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You-- it is against the law to show the swastika, as it is against the law to deny the Holocaust.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's the law in Germany.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Here, you are allowed to, to, to show the swastika.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the two things in an incident, which you asked me to remember was, the ignorance of the-- of even the authorities, about this whole episode, because they don't even know why a swastika should be an irritant to, to anybody, and to Jewish people, especially Jewish people who survived the Holocaust.",
      "word_count": 52
    }
  ],
